- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also a likely category as the proposed approach involves load distribution clusters. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with controlling and managing network resources. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the K-mean++ algorithm is used for clustering. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper involves using machine learning techniques for improving network resource allocation.
